name: Yamato from kantai collection kancolle 大和 艦これ
description:
2023.05.27 updated

retrained model, removed image had rigging and other non-official outfit

also changed the trigger words

  • Recommend weight 0.8~1.0

  • Trigger words and supportive prompts

  • CHARACTER: yamato_\(kancolle\), 1girl,

    ※ Do not use character prompts if you want to get other outfit correctly.

  • ORIGINAL OUTFIT

    • (original_costume), headgear, detached_sleeves, red_skirt, pleated_skirt, black_thighhighs, bare_shoulders,

  • KAINI OUTFIT

    • (kaini_costume), headgear, detached_sleeves, long sleeves, white skirt, pleated skirt, black_highhighs, bare_shoulders, white coat, sleeveless coat, clothing cutout, coat on shoulders, long coat, metal collar, shoulder cutout, collar,

  • CASUAL OUTFIT

    • (spring_costume), alternate costume, official alternate costume, brown sweater, sweater, ribbed_sweater, long_sleeves, white_pants,

  • KIMONO OUTFIT

    • (newyear_costume), japanese_clothes, kimono, long_sleeves, wide_sleeves, obi, headgear, long hair, kimono, sash, floral print,

  • BIKINI OUTFIT

    • (summer_costume), swimsuit, bikini, white_bikini, sarong, official alternate costume, headgear, sandals, thigh_strap, navel, collarbone,

  • KAINI BIKINI

    • (summer2_costume), swimsuit, bikini, white_bikini, pink_bikini, sarong, bracelet, ribbon, hair_ribbon, see-through, navel, collarbone,

Training info

  • based model：nai anime full pruned

  • 101 images for 4 repeats

    • original outfit 20 images

    • kaini outfit 18 images

    • casual outfit 17 images

    • kimono outfit 16 images

    • bikini outfit 15 images

    • kaini bikini 15 images

  • resolution : 768x768

  • rank=32, alpha=16

  • batch size = 2, epochs = 14

  • Optimizer：Lion

  • Learning rate = 3e-5, Unet learning rate = 1.5e-5, Text Encoder learning rate= 3e-5

======= old version =======

Lora of Yamato from kancolle with other alternative outfit

  • Recommend weight around 0.7

  • Recommend to increase the trigger words' weight to get better results

  • Trigger words and supportive prompts

    • CHARACTER

      • yamato_\(kancolle\), 1girl, brown_eyes, brown_hair, large_breasts, long_hair, hair_ornament, ponytail, cherry_blossoms, hair_flower

    • ORIGINAL OUTFIT

      • (yamato_original), headgear, detached_sleeves, red_skirt, pleated_skirt, thighhighs, bare_shoulders,

    • KAINI OUTFIT

      • (yamato_kaini), headgear, detached_sleeves, long_sleeves, white_skirt, pleated_skirt, thighhighs, bare_shoulders,

    • CASUAL OUTFIT

      • (yamato_casual), alternate_costume, sweater, ribbed_sweater, long_sleeves, sidelocks, white_pants,

    • KIMONO OUTFIT

      • (yamato_kimono), japanese_clothes, kimono, long_sleeves, wide_sleeves, obi, headgear,

    • BIKINI OUTFIT

      • (yamato_summer1), swimsuit, white_bikini, sarong, headgear, bare_shoulders, sidelocks, sandals, thigh_strap,

    • KAINI BIKINI

      • (yamato_summer2), alternate_costume, swimsuit, white_bikini, sarong, sidelocks, bracelet, ribbon, hair_ribbon, see-through,

May be difficult to generate kaini bikini outfit perfectly.

Training info

  • based model：Anything v4.5

  • 216 images

    • original outfit 51 images for 4 repeats

    • kaini outfit 22 images for 8 repeats

    • casual outfit 22 images for 8 repeats

    • kimono outfit 18 images for 8 repeats

    • bikini outfit 20 images for 8 repeats

    • kaini bikini 16 images for 8 repeats

    • other outfit 67 images for 2 repeats

  • resolution : 768x768

  • rank=128, alpha=64

  • batch size = 2, epochs = 7

  • Optimizer：AdamW8bit

  • Learning rate = 1e-4, Unet learning rate = 1e-4, Text Encoder learning rate= 5e-5
